This course is gives a detail overview on the history of meteorological measurements in Estonia, on climate forming factors, climatic seasons, spatial, seasonal and interannual variability of climatic variables and trends, climatic regionalization of Estonia. Students will carry out an independent practical research.Objectives/eesmärkid:  This course gives a detail overview on climate forming factors in Estonia, main characteristics of climatic conditions, their territorial and temporal variability in Estonia.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  A student obtains a knowledge on on climate forming factors in Estonia, main characteristics of climatic conditions, their territorial and temporal variability in Estonia, is able to use and process data on the Estonian climate.
